snippet.title: Longplay of SD F-1 Grand Prix
snippet.description:
Longplay of SD F-1 Grand Prix, played as the NTSC-J version on the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. This game's version was released on Oct. 27th, 1995. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

0:00:00 - Start

0:01:02 - America Cup
0:13:15 - Asia Cup
0:25:35 - Europe Cup
0:36:30 - Africa Cup
0:49:50 - The New Challengers
0:50:37 - World Cup
1:06:25 - A. Senna descending from heaven
1:07:10 - Paradise Cup

1:22:31 - Ending + Credits

1:25:30 - World GP Mode
2:21:00 - Ending GP Mode

By: Retro Game Spacko
